    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6217231/" class="title-link">《研究是一门艺术》的读书札记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6217231"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/changzhoujm/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u59648946-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/changzhoujm/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">剑眉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-08-15"
      class="main-meta">2013-08-15 08:38:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6217231_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   今天笔记完了《研究是一门艺术》，感觉到后面有一些草草了事了。似乎演变成了为摘而摘。我对于这一本书，似乎缺乏整体的架构、整体的概念。为什么？然后下午的关于《教育就是解放心灵》这本书同样也是变成了这样的一种行为。我发现自己的阅读容易被细节拘泥。于是放下了摘录精...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6217231_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6217231_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评21篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
