  <h2>
    <span class="">在哪儿借这本书</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <ul class="bs more-after">
      
      <li style="border: none">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fipac.library.sh.cn%2Fipac20%2Fipac.jsp%3Faspect%3Dbasic_search%26profile%3Dsl%26index%3DISBN%26term%3D9787501189045&amp;subject=7501189048&amp;type=borrow&amp;library=10012&amp;link2key=d9b7391f22" target="_blank">上海市中心图书馆(12)</a>
